	"A New Method for Detecting Differential Item Functioning in the Rasch Model.",
 	"Technical Report 92.",
 	"Department of Statistics, Ludwig-Maximilians-Universitaet Muenchen.",
	"URL http://epub.ub.uni-muenchen.de/11915/"),
	
